<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/userBoard/joinForm.css">
    <title>회원가입</title>

</head>

<body>


    <div class="login-container">

        <div class="loginMainLogo">
            <h1>wanted</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="mainSlogan">
            하나의 계정으로 <br>
            더욱 편리하게
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="subSlogan">
            원티드가 제공하는 서비스를 <br>
            하나의 계정으로 모두 이용할 수 있습니다.
        </div>

        <form id="login-form" action="/userjoin" method="post">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="username">Username:</label>
                <input type="text" id="username" name="loginId" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="password">Password:</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
            </div>

            <hr>
            <br>


            <button class="btn" type="submit">회원가입</button>

            <br>

            <div class="bottomFooter">이용약관
                <span style="font-weight: bold;"> 개인정보처리방침</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bottomFooter">@Wantedlab, Inc.
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>


</body>

</html>